@page "/music"

<PageTitle>Music</PageTitle>

<div class="music-page">
    <img src="/images/LogoJellyfish.png"
         alt=""
         class="music-backdrop"
         aria-hidden="true" />

    <div class="music-content">
        <h1>Music</h1>

        <p class="music-intro">
            Thrive In Chaos is a five-piece rock band that blends atmospheric soundscapes with dynamic guitar work, creating music that shifts between calm, immersive layers and heavier, high-energy moments. Their songs draw from a wide range of rock influences while embracing the open, expansive feel often found in post-rock.

            Fueled by passion and a relentless drive to evolve, Thrive In Chaos is gearing up to push further, play louder, and take on even bigger stages.
        </p>

        <h2>Genres</h2>
        <ul class="music-genres">
            <li>Post-Rock</li>
            <li>Alternative Rock</li>
            <li>Stoner Rock</li>
            <li>Progressive</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Latest Release</h2>

        <div class="latest-release">
            <img src="/images/Music/Salvation.png"
                 alt="Latest release cover"
                 class="latest-release-cover" />

            <div class="latest-release-info">
                <h3>SALVATION</h3>
                <p>
                    Out Now!
                </p>

                <div class="stream-buttons">
                    <a class="stream-btn stream-btn-spotify"
                       href="https://open.spotify.com/track/2YnDysr1DgOL3nHZudvTfX?si=dc2143918ef34105"
                       target="_blank"
                       rel="noopener noreferrer">
                        <i class="bi bi-spotify"></i>
                        Stream now
                    </a>

                    <a class="stream-btn stream-btn-youtube"
                       href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xT-E-y2JOV0"
                       target="_blank"
                       rel="noopener noreferrer">
                        <i class="bi bi-youtube"></i>
                        Stream now
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>